QUESTION-4

Create a duplicate table of EMPLOYEE.


Query:

mysql>create table emp select * from employee;

mysql> desc emp;
+-----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| Field     | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
